    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/7e32910ba58cd07d8055091e2ce8d38e.avif?t=1759341257\" width=614 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/ad26db0a94f054faaa8256ab308be87f.poster.avif?t=1759341257\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/ad26db0a94f054faaa8256ab308be87f.webm?t=1759341257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/ad26db0a94f054faaa8256ab308be87f.mp4?t=1759341257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Demon Lord, who rules over and manages his Dungeon.<br>Listen to what Creatures have to say to you, then make a Yes or No decision. <br>Each decision can affect your Dungeon's stats (Minion Count, Minion Loyalty, Karma and/or Gold). <br>Will you succeed in growing your Dungeon, or will you make it fall? <br>The choice is yours. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/1d31e21cb58f07fd9095a77b19da76f5.avif?t=1759341257\" width=614 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/1fd145806f78bd15be52d330e9fc5072.poster.avif?t=1759341257\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/1fd145806f78bd15be52d330e9fc5072.webm?t=1759341257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/1fd145806f78bd15be52d330e9fc5072.mp4?t=1759341257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Add, Change or Remove Game Content (Creatures, Day Events, Textures, Music, etc.) using the Content Packs (Addon + Resource Pack) System.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/52650081ecdfb8005a4e53b7649a4b0b.avif?t=1759341257\" width=614 height=120 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/61be00d89dd0fab9c697b60e05180c25.poster.avif?t=1759341257\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/61be00d89dd0fab9c697b60e05180c25.webm?t=1759341257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056660/extras/61be00d89dd0fab9c697b60e05180c25.mp4?t=1759341257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Day events can start at the end of a Day, before your Daily Report. Some can randomly happen each day, and some will only happen once a Creature's specific dialog has been said. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >97 Characters and 50 Day Events currently added</h2>",
